OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CWales' PCC election this week
OL,6,FOn May 2, elections will take place
OL,7,Fthat will shape the future of policing
OL,8,Fin Wales.
OL,10,FWhile residents across some part of
OL,11,Fthe United Kingdom will take part in
OL,12,Flocal council elections or mayoral
OL,13,Felections, Wales will only have polls
OL,14,Ffor the next Police and Crime
OL,15,FCommissioners.
OL,17,FITV Wales' explains what these
OL,18,Felections entail and why they are
OL,19,Fdifferent this year.
