OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CWales' PCC election this week
OL,6,FWhat are Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioners (PCCs)?
OL,9,FPCCs have been part of the Welsh
OL,10,Flandscape since 2012. They set the
OL,11,Fpolice budget, they employ the Chief
OL,12,FConstable and they work closely with
OL,13,Fcouncils and community organisations
OL,14,Fon police plans.
OL,16,FWales has four Police and Crime
OL,17,FCommissioners - one for each policing
OL,18,Farea. North Wales, Dyfed Powys, South
OL,19,FWales and Gwent.
