OL,6,FWho is standing in the May 2024
OL,7,Felection?
OL,9,FEach of the four main parties in Wales
OL,10,F- Labour, Conservatives, Plaid Cymru
OL,11,Fand Liberal Democrats are fielding
OL,12,Fcandidates in each area.
OL,14,FWhat is the turnout of Police and
OL,15,FCrime Commissioner elections?
OL,17,FThe last time PCC elections took place
OL,18,Fin Wales on their own (without local
OL,19,Fcouncil elections at the same time)
OL,20,Fturnout was just 14.9%.
