OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CWales' PCC election this week
OL,6,FThe last two PCC elections coincided
OL,7,Fwith the Senedd elections and turnout
OL,8,Fwas a lot higher.
OL,10,FIn 2021, the highest turnout was in
OL,11,FDyfed-Powys (50.6%), North Wales
OL,12,F(45.4%), South Wales (43.9%) and Gwent
OL,13,F(41%).
OL,15,FITV Wales asked members of the public
OL,16,Fwhat they think of the upcoming polls.
OL,18,F"I won't be voting, I don't think it's
OL,19,Fa valid reason to vote," one said.
