OL,6,FAnother told our reporter: "It's
OL,7,Freally hard to have an opinion, I've
OL,8,Fhad no information through my front
OL,9,Fdoor. So I've been thinking 'will I or
OL,10,Fwon't I vote?' Because I know nothing
OL,11,Fabout the candidates."
OL,13,FA third constituent added: "When the
OL,14,Fgovernment seems to be short of money,
OL,15,Fin various areas, it seems a lot of
OL,16,Fmoney to spend on the position and the
OL,17,Felection process, it's so costly. Just
OL,18,Fseems like a bit of a waste of time."
OL,20,FWhat is different this time?
