OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CWales' PCC election this week
OL,6,FUnlike previous elections in Wales,
OL,7,Fthis will be the first time voter ID
OL,8,Fis required.
OL,10,FJess Blair, Director of Electoral
OL,11,FReform Society Cymru, said it's the
OL,12,F"biggest change for a really long
OL,13,Ftime."
OL,15,FShe added: "That presents a massive
OL,16,Frisk. A lot of people don't have
OL,17,Faccess to voter ID.
