OL,6,F"A lot of the ID that is accepted -
OL,7,Fdriver's license and passport - costs
OL,8,Fmoney to get. So it's a bit of a
OL,9,Fdiscriminatory policy."
OL,11,FHow effective are Police and Crime
OL,12,FCommissioners?
OL,14,F"It's really difficult to say,"
OL,15,Faccording to Professor Martin Innes,
OL,16,FDirector of the Crime and Security
OL,17,FResearch Institute at Cardiff
OL,18,FUniversity.
