OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CWales' PCC election this week
OL,6,FHe told Sharp End: "The whole system
OL,7,Fis designed to generate local plans
OL,8,Fand local solutions. So different
OL,9,FPolice and Crime Commissioners are
OL,10,Fdoing different things.
OL,12,F"My broad assessment would be -
OL,13,Flooking across England and Wales - I
OL,14,Fthink about a third of Police and
OL,15,FCrime Commissioners have been
OL,16,Feffective, a third have been average
OL,17,Fand a third really haven't made a
OL,18,Fsignificant impact in terms of
OL,19,Fchanging the delivery of policing on
OL,20,Fthe ground."
