OL,6,FWhat challenges will the elected
OL,7,FPolice and Crime Commissioners face?
OL,9,FProf Innes said: "The biggest priority
OL,10,Fis trying to restore public trust and
OL,11,Fconfidence, and to do that against a
OL,12,Fvery challenging political and
OL,13,Feconomic climate, where no doubt
OL,14,Fpolicing will be highly contentious.
OL,16,F"At the same time where everybody is
OL,17,Fgrappling with the new kinds of crime
OL,18,Fthat are coming through like online
OL,19,Fharms and cyber fraud."
